===Noun===

A minimalist form of undergarment that snugly embraces the hips (as a belt would) and being connected from front to back (due South) by a triangular and progressively thinning piece of material, thus covering a decreasing portion of the genitals, as one moves from front to back, resulting in a complete exposure of the "butt cheeks" on both sides. Also known as a thong or in some languages "tanga", this particular piece of clothing can, on the right person, be incredibly arousing, or deplorably disgusting, or for some very sick persons, both. On the wrong person, all bets are off. Made famous by samba dancers in Brazil. Got Bill Clinton in trouble for obvious (albeit all the right) reasons. Synonyms: Thong, Tanga, Butt Floss. Antonyms: boxer shorts, jockey shorts, briefs, tighty-whites, Texas butt-huggers, Bakersfield Browns, and all other forms of normal or otherwise retro-type, boxers, everyday underwear that you're embarassed about even when your mom sees 'em.